OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F395A1779815153
OL,3,CFamily pay tribute to woman found dead
OL,4,Cin flat
OL,6,FThe family of a woman believed to have
OL,7,Fbeen murdered have paid tribute to her
OL,8,Fsaying they will always love her.
OL,10,FKeeley Apsinall, 44, was found in a
OL,11,Fflat on the Freehold estate, on
OL,12,FTweedale Street, in Rochdale on 26 May
OL,13,Fafter Greater Manchester Police was
OL,14,Fcalled out following a concern for
OL,15,Fwelfare. She died at the scene.
OL,17,FPaying tribute to Keeley, known to
OL,18,Ffriends as Kiki, her family said:
OL,19,F"Gone too soon.. we can't believe you
OL,20,Fare gone.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/4
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,396,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39502
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F395A1779815153
OL,3,CFamily pay tribute to woman found dead
OL,4,Cin flat
OL,6,F"We will always love you and miss you,
OL,7,Flove all your family xx."
OL,9,FA man in his 30s has been arrested on
OL,10,Fsuspicion of murder and remains in
OL,11,Fcustody for questioning.
OL,13,FTemporary Detective Chief
OL,14,FSuperintendent Jamie Daniels, from
OL,15,FGMP's Major Incident Team: "We
OL,16,Fappreciate this incident is likely to
OL,17,Fcause some distress amongst the public
OL,18,Fand local community.
OL,26,@oD@YO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/4
